(74, 1, '2024-02-17 02:11:53', '2024-02-19 02:25:12', 1, 'Taxation Services', 'taxation-services', '<h4 class=\\\"h-edit\\\"><b>Tax Preparation Services In Toronto </b> </h4>\r\n<p class=\\\"text-color\\\"> There may be more questions than answers when it comes to preparing your own income tax return. A research conducted by the General Accounting Office of the US Government found that the majority of taxpayers, or 77% of the 71 million taxpayers, felt that hiring a professional tax preparer had been beneficial to them.\r\n\r\n    Whether we like it or not, the complexity of today\\\'s tax regulations may make even relatively simple returns challenging to file. It is far too simple to forget about credits and deductions to which you are legally entitled. Use of computer software programs is not a replacement for the guidance of a qualified tax professional. </p>\r\n<p class=\\\"text-color\\\"> Don\\\'t panic if you own a small business and haven\\\'t kept up with your bookkeeping. We are able to assist you. We will prepare your personal income tax return, a complete Schedule C, and your year\\\'s worth of accounting. Next, we\\\'ll assist you in putting up a simple system that will enable you to maintain impeccable records for the upcoming year.\r\n    \r\n     </p>\r\n<h4 class=\\\"h-edit\\\"><b>This is what you receive... </b></h4>\r\n<div class=\\\"flex\\\">\r\n<div><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><li>Our computer software will evaluate your tax return multiple times, looking for possible issues the IRS might look into more closely and cross-referencing the calculations to reduce IRS correspondence.</li></ul> </div> \r\n<div><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><li>You can file your tax return electronically to expedite the processing of your refund.</li></ul> </div>\r\n<div><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><li>To receive more money back each week, our experts will demonstrate to you how to modify you