(20, 0, '2023-08-28 04:23:23', '2023-09-04 04:32:58', 2, 2, 'Declarations', 'logo-image-spiders', 'declarations', 'Canada Visa Declaration: Applicant Affirms Accuracy Of Provided Information.', '<div class=\\\"text-color\\\">\r\nYou can make your customs and immigration declaration using Advance Declaration in the ArriveCAN app before you fly into one of Canada\\\'s participating airports. Upon arrival:\r\nconfirm (certify) your declaration at a kiosk or eGate – it\\\'s 30% faster, take advantage of Advance Declaration express lanes.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\\\"text-dark mt-3\\\"><b>How to submit your Advance Declaration</b></h1>\r\n<h4 class=\\\"text-dark\\\">Following these four steps</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\\\"step mt-3\\\"><span class=\\\"step-box\\\">01</span>Sign in to the ArriveCAN app or the web version online and follow the prompts</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\\\"step mt-3\\\"><span class=\\\"step-box\\\">02</span>Confirm your travel identity document information</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\\\"step mt-3\\\"><span class=\\\"step-box\\\">03</span>Answer the customs and immigration questions truthfully</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\\\"step mt-3\\\"><span class=\\\"step-box\\\">04</span>Submit the declaration 72 hours prior to arriving in Canada</h4>\r\n\r\nWhen you are done:\r\n\r\n<ul class=\\\"list\\\"><li>a confirmation screen should appear, acknowledging a successful submission</li><li>you will receive a confirmation email and a reference number</li></ul>\r\n</div>'),
(21, 0, '2023-08-28 04:43:06', '2024-02-05 00:56:20', 1, 2, 'Personal Taxes', 'logo-image-spiders', 'personal-taxes', 'Family Law Services: The Law Office of Jahedul Law\\\'s attorneys are dedicated to helping their clients move on into the greatest possible lives for themselves and their family by assisting them in successfully navigating legal changes. Our founder and lead attorney, Mr. Jahedul Islam, has more than 20 years of experience in family law, mediation, and civil litigation.', '<div class=\\\"text-color\\\"><p style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\\\"><h4><b>The attorneys of the Law Office of Jahedul Law.</b></h4> are committed to one goal helping our clients successfully navigate legal transitions and move forward into the life that is best for them and their families.<br><br><br><br> <h4 style=\\\"text-align: left !important;\\\">Attorney Mr. Jahedul Islam,</h4> our founder and primary attorney, has over twenty years of experience in civil litigation, mediation, and family law.</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\\\">We never lose sight of you or your needs. We take the time to pay close attention to your worries, assist you in setting objectives, considering your options, and creating a case-specific legal plan. The appropriate course of action for you may involve mediation or regular court procedures (litigation), depending on your particular situation. We have the flexibility and expertise to act in your best interests because of our extensive and varied experience. \r\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><b>Among our procedures are:<b></h4></p>\r\n<ul style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outli