weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">grounds for a divorce petition.</li>\r\n<li style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 17.008px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">financial issues following a divorce or separation.</li>\r\n<li style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 17.008px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">examination of pension and tax issues.</li>\r\n<li style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 17.008px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">Issues related to jurisdiction and international relations.</li>\r\n<li style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 17.008px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">Restrictive orders and injunctions.</li>\r\n<li style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 17.008px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">Living together and prenuptial agreements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><b>When it came to children, our areas of guidance and support encompassed:</b></h4>\r\n<ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\\\">\r\n<li style=\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 17.008px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">Concerns about child custody and maintenance payments.</li>\r\n<li style=\\\"border: 0px;