(494, '2024-01-20 06:58:31', 1, 'services', 22, '{\"changed\":{\"description\":[\"<div class=\\\\\\\"text-color\\\\\\\">\\r\\nWelcome to the Ontario Court of Justice\\\\\'s guide to Canadian immigration and legal services inc.! Whether you\\\\\'re a newcomer looking to make Ontario your home or seeking guidance on immigration processes, we\\\\\'re here to help. Our aim is to provide you with valuable information and resources to make your immigration journey as smooth as possible.\\r\\n\\r\\nUnder Canada\\u2019s immigration law, you can ask the Federal Court of Canada to review immigration decisions.\\r\\n\\r\\nThere are deadlines to apply for a review. For example, if the Immigration and Refugee Board (IRB) rejects your claim for refugee protection, you must file an application for a Federal Court review within 15 days of the IRB decision. If you want to apply for a review, you may want to get legal advice as soon as possible.\\r\\n\\r\\nA review by the Federal Court is a 2-stage process:\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul class=\\\\\\\"list\\\\\\\"><li>Leave stage<\\/li><li>Judicial review stage<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<h4 class=\\\\\\\"step mt-3\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"step-box\\\\\\\">01<\\/span>Leave<\\/h4>\\r\\nIn the first stage, called the leave stage, the Court reviews the documents about your case. You must show the Court that the decision was not fair or reasonable , or that there was an error.\\r\\nIf the Court gives leave, it means it agrees to examine the decision in depth.\\r\\n<h4 class=\\\\\\\"step mt-3\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"step-box\\\\\\\">02<\\/span>Judicial review<\\/h4>\\r\\nThe second stage is called the judicial review. At this stage, you (with or without a lawyer) can attend an oral hearing before the Court and explain why you believe the original IRB decision was wrong.\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"<div class=\\\\\\\"text-color\\\\\\\">\\r\\nWelcome to the Ontario Court of Justice\\\\\'s guide to Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions, Inc.! Whether you\\\\\'re a newcomer looking to make Ontario your home or seeking guidance on immigration processes, we\\\\\'re here to help. Our aim is to provide you with valuable information and resources to make your immigration journey as smooth as possible.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nA tax lawyer is often an attorney whose practice is concentrated on tax matters, such as the Goods and Services Tax (GST), Retail Sales Tax (RST\\/PST), Personal or Corporate Income Tax, Harmonized Sales Tax (HST), and the Ontario Employer Health Tax (EHT).\\r\\n\\r\\nA tax attorney frequently represents clients in front of numerous governmental bodies (audits, objections, appeals). A large number of these attorneys will also represent clients in Canadian Tax Court appeals.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nWhile some tax lawyers specialize in a range of tax sectors, others could only concentrate on one tax category. A tax lawyer will typically know more about tax law than a regular practitioner.\\r\\n\\r\\nNumerous tax attorneys at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Inc.\\u00a0are knowledgeable in all of these fields and are available to represent you before the Canada Revenue Agency (CRA) and other government agencies. For any tax-related issues, the tax attorneys at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Inc.\\u00a0can also defend you before the Tax Court of Canada, the Federal Court of Appeal, and the Supreme Court of Canada.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe ability to handle all of our non-resident clients\\\\\' Canadian tax and trade issues in one sitting, with just one of our partners, is something we believe gives us a competitive advantage. All of Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Inc\\\\\'s tax lawyers are also knowledgeable in other areas of our practice, such as customs and trade-related matters.\\r\\n<\\/div>\"],\"users_id\":[2,1]},\"moreInfo\":[]}'),
(495, '2024-01-20 07:16:46', 1, 'services', 21, '{\"changed\":{\"name\":[\"Documents Attestations\",\"Accounting & Bookkeeping Services\"],\"uri_value\":[\"documents-attestations\",\"accounting-and-bookkeeping-services-\"],\"short_description\":[\"An Attestation Is A Certification That A Document and The Signatures Within Are Valid.\",\"Accounting & Bookkeeping Services\\\\\\\" refers to professional services provided to businesses and individuals to manage their financial records, transactions, and compliance with accounting and tax regulations. These services are essential for maintaining accurate and up-to-date financial information, ensuring compliance with tax laws, and making informed business decisions.\"],\"description\":[\"<div class=\\\\\\\"text-color\\\\\\\">\\r\\nAttesting documents is crucial for the credibility of the documents when applying for a Canadian visa. Here\\\\\'s a breakdown of the process and types of documents that might require attestation: <br><br><br> \\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b>ACCOUNTING AND BOOKKEEPING SERVICES<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nLet the certified tax accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada help you with all your business tax accounting and bookkeeping services and save on your business taxes. Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions provides synergistic tax accounting, bookkeeping, tax planning and financial planning services for businesses of all sizes\\r\\n\\r\\nSimple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada has locations (by appointment only) in Mississauga, Toronto, and Markham to serve you. You can also have one of our certified tax accountants assist you with your back tax and tax audit needs remotely from the comfort of your home, utilizing Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada\\\\\'s secure document transfer portal. We accept clients from Canada and worldwide. \\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b>THE IMPORTANCE OF BOOKKEEPING FOR YOUR BUSINESS<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nGood financial records help a business increase its profit. Good record-keeping allows the business owner to make decisions based on the financial results of the business. It allows you to concentrate on profitable segments of your business and make the decisions that will grow it. Heed the old adage, \\u201cMost businesses fail because of poor financial management.\\u201d\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b> BOOKKEEPING AND TAX<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nIn addition to improved financial management, good bookkeeping will keep the \\u201ctax man\\u201d off your back. What business owners sometimes do is fall behind in accounting and bookkeeping and don\\u2019t file their tax returns for multiple years. Then, the business owner gets an ominous letter in the mail from the tax department requesting that you file tax returns. You will inevitably be stressed out, scrambling for receipts, scrambling for your financial records, and losing precious business management time. If you don\\u2019t respond to the tax filing letters, the tax department will garnish wages, seize assets, and put a lien on your properties. All of these issues, combined, can ruin a business. Don\\u2019t let this happen to you! Contact the accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada for your bookkeeping and accounting, and focus on growing your business.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b> ADDITIONAL TAX ACCOUNTING AND TAX PLANNING<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nThe certified accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada can also provide assistance with your business tax preparation, tax planning, and personal tax preparation. Our parent company, GTA Wealth Management Inc.,\\u00a0can provide synergistic assistance with financial services such as investments, insurance, and mortgages. Why not save yourself time and money and get all your bookkeeping, tax preparation, tax planning, and financial services from one full-service location?\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b> GET PROFESSIONAL TAX ACCOUNTING AND BOOKKEEPING HELP<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nLet the certified tax accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada help you with all your