(500, '2024-01-20 07:32:43', 1, 'services', 31, '{\"changed\":{\"name\":[\"Detention Review Appeals\",\"Corporate Tax Advice & Planning\"],\"uri_value\":[\"detention-review-appeals\",\"corporate-tax-advice-and-planning\"],\"short_description\":[\"Legal Processes Where Detained Individuals Challenge Their Detention Based On Various Grounds, Seeking Release or Improved Conditions.\",\"Corporate Tax Advice & Planning refers to the specialized services provided by tax professionals to help businesses navigate the complex landscape of corporate taxation. This aspect of accounting and tax services focuses on developing strategies to optimize a company\\\\\'s tax position while ensuring compliance with relevant tax laws and regulations.\"],\"description\":[\"<div class=\\\\\\\"text-color\\\\\\\">\\r\\nDetention review appeals typically refer to legal processes or procedures where individuals who are detained by immigration authorities or law enforcement agencies can appeal their detention. These appeals are generally used in situations where individuals believe their detention is unjust or illegal. The specific process and rules for detention review appeals can vary by country and jurisdiction. \\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b> CORPORATE TAX ADVICE & PLANNING <\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nOur Corporate Tax Advice group offers a comprehensive range of tax advisory services for all types of clients, from multinational public corporations to regional entrepreneurial enterprises.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe service all sectors of the economy including telecommunications, mining, real estate development, and manufacturing through a diversified and highly experienced team of dedicated tax advisors.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe provide sophisticated yet practical solutions to the unique challenges faced by business entities and their respective owners. Our corporate advisory services encompass all aspects of tax-related business planning, including corporate reorganizations and consolidations, mergers and acquisitions, divestitures, structured finance, and tax-driven transactions. Examined together with executive remuneration, shareholder taxation, and corporate governance ramifications, we provide a fully integrated approach to corporate taxation planning, whether transactional, operational, or structural.\\r\\n\\r\\nOur advice extends beyond Canada as part of our broad cross-border and international tax planning practice. We routinely assist clients located in various and varied foreign jurisdictions who are investing or otherwise carrying on business in Canada, as well as Canadian-based businesses with operations abroad. We possess both the knowledge and experience to address all aspects of Canadian tax planning for business enterprises.\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"<div class=\\\\\\\"text-color\\\\\\\">\\r\\nCorporate Tax Advice & Planning refers to the specialized services provided by tax professionals to help businesses navigate the complex landscape of corporate taxation. This aspect of accounting and tax services focuses on developing strategies to optimize a company\\\\\'s tax position while ensuring compliance with relevant tax laws and regulations.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b> CORPORATE TAX ADVICE & PLANNING <\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nOur Corporate Tax Advice group offers a comprehensive range of tax advisory services for all types of clients, from multinational public corporations to regional entrepreneurial enterprises.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe service all sectors of the economy including telecommunications, mining, real estate development, and manufacturing through a diversified and highly experienced team of dedicated tax advisors.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe provide sophisticated yet practical solutions to the unique challenges faced by business entities and their respective owners. Our corporate advisory services encompass all aspects of tax-related business planning, including corporate reorganizations and consolidations, mergers and acquisitions, divestitures, structured finance, and tax-driven transactions. Examined toge