(540, '2024-02-04 23:56:34', 1, 'services', 21, '{\"changed\":{\"name\":[\"Accounting & Bookkeeping\",\"Family Law\"],\"uri_value\":[\"accounting-and-bookkeeping-services\",\"family-law\"],\"short_description\":[\"Accounting & Bookkeeping Services\\\\\\\" refers to professional services provided to businesses and individuals to manage their financial records, transactions, and compliance with accounting and tax regulations. These services are essential for maintaining accurate and up-to-date financial information, ensuring compliance with tax laws, and making informed business decisions.\",\"Family Law Services: The Law Office of Jahedul Law\\\\\'s attorneys are dedicated to helping their clients move on into the greatest possible lives for themselves and their family by assisting them in successfully navigating legal changes. Our founder and lead attorney, Mr. Jahedul Islam, has more than 20 years of experience in family law, mediation, and civil litigation.\"],\"description\":[\"<div class=\\\\\\\"text-color\\\\\\\">\\r\\nAccounting & Bookkeeping Services\\\\\\\" refers to professional services provided to businesses and individuals to manage their financial records, transactions, and compliance with accounting and tax regulations. These services are essential for maintaining accurate and up-to-date financial information, ensuring compliance with tax laws. <br><br><br> \\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b>ACCOUNTING AND BOOKKEEPING SERVICES<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nLet the certified tax accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada help you with all your business tax accounting and bookkeeping services and save on your business taxes. Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions provides synergistic tax accounting, bookkeeping, tax planning and financial planning services for businesses of all sizes\\r\\n\\r\\nSimple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada has locations (by appointment only) in Mississauga, Toronto, and Markham to serve you. You can also have one of our certified tax accountants assist you with your back tax and tax audit needs remotely from the comfort of your home, utilizing Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada\\\\\'s secure document transfer portal. We accept clients from Canada and worldwide. \\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"text-align: left;\\\\\\\"><b>THE IMPORTANCE OF BOOKKEEPING FOR YOUR BUSINESS<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nGood financial records help a business increase its profit. Good record-keeping allows the business owner to make decisions based on the financial results of the business. It allows you to concentrate on profitable segments of your business and make the decisions that will grow it. Heed the old adage, \\u201cMost businesses fail because of poor financial management.\\u201d\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b> BOOKKEEPING AND TAX<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nIn addition to improved financial management, good bookkeeping will keep the \\u201ctax man\\u201d off your back. What business owners sometimes do is fall behind in accounting and bookkeeping and don\\u2019t file their tax returns for multiple years. Then, the business owner gets an ominous letter in the mail from the tax department requesting that you file tax returns. You will inevitably be stressed out, scrambling for receipts, scrambling for your financial records, and losing precious business management time. If you don\\u2019t respond to the tax filing letters, the tax department will garnish wages, seize assets, and put a lien on your properties. All of these issues, combined, can ruin a business. Don\\u2019t let this happen to you! Contact the accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada for your bookkeeping and accounting, and focus on growing your business.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b> ADDITIONAL TAX ACCOUNTING AND TAX PLANNING<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nThe certified accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada can also provide assistance with your business tax preparation, tax planning, and personal tax preparation. Our parent company, GTA Wealth Management Inc.,\\u00a0can provide synergistic assistance with financial services such as investments, insurance, and mortgages. Why not save yourself time and money and get all your bookkeeping, tax preparation, tax planning, and financial services from one full-service location?\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"text-align: left;\\\\\\\"><b> GET PROFESSIONAL TAX ACCOUNTING AND BOOKKEEPING HELP<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nLet the certified tax accountants at Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada help you with all your business tax accounting and bookkeeping services and save on your business taxes.\\r\\n\\r\\nSimple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada has three\\u00a0locations\\u00a0(by appointment only) in Mississauga, Toronto, and Markham to serve you. You can also have one of our certified tax accountants assist you with your back tax and tax audit needs remotely from the comfort of your home, utilizing Simple Accounting & Tax Solutions Canada\\\\\'s secure document transfer portal. We accept clients from Canada and worldwide.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><b>FREE INITIAL PHONE CONSULTATION<\\/b><\\/h4>\\r\\nSimple Accounting & Tax Solutions Inc. Canada offers a stress-free initial phone consultation with one of our professional certified tax accountants. We welcome your business!\\r\\nContact Us at <b>(647) 867-6351<\\/b>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"<div class=\\\\\\\"text-color\\\\\\\"><p style=\\\\\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\\\\\\\">The attorneys of the Law Office of Jahedul Law. are committed to one goal helping our clients successfully navigate legal transitions and move forward into the life that is best for them and their families. Attorney Mr. Jahedul Islam, our founder and primary attorney, has over twenty years of experience in civil litigation, mediation, and family law.<\\/p><p style=\\\\\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outline: 