n-line: underline; color: rgb(58, 74, 133);\\\\\\\">Mediation<\\/a>&nbsp;(for both family law and other civil matters)<\\/li><li style=\\\\\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 17.008px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\\\\\"><a href=\\\\\\\"https:\\/\\/www.jahedullaw.ca\\/practice-areas\\/estate-planning\\/\\\\\\\" data-wpel-link=\\\\\\\"internal\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(58, 74, 133);\\\\\\\">Estate Planning<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\\\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\\\\\\\">In addition to helping you with ancillary issues that frequently accompany family law cases, like the need to revise an estate plan or transfer real estate, our attorneys will mentor and defend you throughout your case. We are still available to collaborate with you to advance and defend your interests in the event that questions about interpretation, enforcement, or change arise after your case is concluded.<\\/p><p style=\\\\\\\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 17.008px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\\\\\\\">We invite you to&nbsp;<a href=\\\\\\\"https:\\/\\/www.jahedullaw.ca\\/contact-us\\/\\\\\\\" data-wpel-link=\\\\\\\"internal\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(58, 74, 133);\\\\\\\">contact us<\\/a>&nbsp;to schedule a comprehensive consultation to discuss your needs. We serve clients in Ontario and the surrounding area. We look forward to working with you.<\\/p><\\/div>\"]},\"moreInfo\":[]}');
